<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es" class="h-full">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %> | KeyHub</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body class="min-h-full flex flex-col bg-gray-50">
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <div class="flex-1 py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-700 to-primary-800 rounded-full mb-6 shadow-xl">
          <svg class="w-14 h-14 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 7a2 2 0 012 2m4 0a6 6 0 01-7.743 5.743L11 17H9v2H7v2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-2.586a1 1 0 01.293-.707l5.964-5.964A6 6 0 1121 9z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h1 class="section-header text-center"><%= title %></h1>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-8 mb-8">
        <h3 class="section-subheader">Nuestra Misión</h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-navy-700 mb-4">
          KeyHub es la plataforma líder en gestión de inmuebles en Argentina. 
          Conectamos a propietarios, inquilinos y compradores de manera segura y eficiente.
        </p>
        <p class="text-navy-600">
          Nuestra misión es facilitar el proceso de búsqueda, alquiler y compra de propiedades, 
          ofreciendo una experiencia transparente y confiable para todos nuestros usuarios.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-8 mb-8">
        <h3 class="section-subheader">¿Por qué elegirnos?</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-700 to-primary-800 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Seguridad</h5>
              <p class="text-navy-600">Todas las transacciones y datos están protegidos con los más altos estándares de seguridad.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-cyan to-accent-teal rounded-lg shadow-md">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Búsqueda Avanzada</h5>
              <p class="text-navy-600">Encuentra exactamente lo que buscas con nuestros filtros inteligentes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-emerald to-accent-teal rounded-lg shadow-md">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Comunidad</h5>
              <p class="text-navy-600">Miles de usuarios confían en nosotros para sus necesidades inmobiliarias.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-amber to-accent-orange rounded-lg shadow-md">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 5.636l-3.536 3.536m0 5.656l3.536 3.536M9.172 9.172L5.636 5.636m3.536 9.192l-3.536 3.536M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-5 0a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Soporte 24/7</h5>
              <p class="text-navy-600">Nuestro equipo está disponible para ayudarte en todo momento.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-8">
        <h3 class="section-subheader">Contacto</h3>
        <div class="space-y-3 mb-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-navy-700">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Email:</strong> info@keyhub.com</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-navy-700">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Teléfono:</strong> +54 11 1234-5678</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-navy-700">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"></path>
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Dirección:</strong> Buenos Aires, Argentina</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
          </svg>
          Contáctanos
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
